data.description: Up to $10,000 in cost assistance.  You will lose yourself in this beautiful 3 story.  Completely rewired and renovated in 2008, featuring Pella Windows and including a 28X14, 3 story rear addition.   2 Zone heating and AC.   From the moment you walk into a large foyer you will fall in love with original pocket doors to the LR.  Adjoining DR and LR both have original hardwood floors.  Family Room is next which adjoins the modernized kitchen with beautiful dble doors leading to the completely private and large dble lot which is surrounded by privacy fencing.  Kitchen comes complete with SS appliances (5 burner stove, micro, dble DW and Fridge).  Full Bath and Walk-In Pantry complete the main floor.  Second Floor consist of 4 bdrm.  Primary Bdrm very private as it is separated by a dressing room, hallway (which houses the W/D) and Full Bath.  If that is enough, wait til you see the size of the 3rd floor finished bonus room.  Pictures do not do this home justice!!
